snippet.title: The Walking Dead : 400 Days Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The Walking Dead: 400 Days is here this week - and we have release dates!

Tuesday, July 2nd -- PlayStation Network(SCEA, North America)
Wednesday, July 3rd -- PC/Mac (Steam, Telltale Games Store, Worldwide)
Friday, July 5th -- Xbox Live (Worldwide)
Wednesday, July 10th -- PlayStation Network (SCEE, Europe)
Thursday, July 11th -- iOS App Store (Worldwide)


Website: http://www.telltalegames.com/walkingdead
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/TheWalkingDeadGame
Twitter: https://twitter.com/#!/telltalegames
